Name: Only Society: Arena
About the game: Only Society Arena is an MOBA game which players will play in a third person view with choosing either in team ranger or team rogue to defend each base. Damaging the player health to empty will stun the player. Knocking out the player from the platform will eliminate the player regardless the health. Start rolling your sleeves and join the battle.
